          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1682082076648-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chicken tamarind curry </strong>over the <strong>turmeric rice</strong></p><p>Dollop your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> over the top and garnish with the <strong>remaining nigella seeds</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
